n ihren organisationalen Strukturen wie spezifischen Veränderungsbedarfen hinsichtlich Interkultureller Öffnung analysiert.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 17. Dez 2021) 0aManagementxSocial aspects. 4aChancengleichheit. 4aEinwanderung. 4aIntegration. 4aInterkulturelles Management. 4aMigration. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Sociology / General.2bisacsh1 aBenikowski, Bernd, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFocali, Ergin, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGriese, Christiane, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGriese, Christiane, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aHagemann, Tim, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHöhne, Steffen, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKarakaþodlu, Yasemin, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMarburger, Helga, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMarburger, Helga, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aMeier-Braun, Karl-Heinz, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRothe, Karin, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSauer, Martin, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSchilder, Michael, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSchmidt, Andrea, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSzoldatits, Franziska, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aUslucan, Haci-Halil, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aVaudt, Susanne, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aWilleke, Rita, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc